.fi
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.B citron 
is a __xservername__ input driver for 
.I Citron Infrared Touch
devices.
.PP
The
.B citron
driver acts as a pointer input device, and may be used as the
X server's core pointer. It is connected via a "RS232" with the host.
