.BI "Option ""PressPitchKey"" """ value """
This value determines the pitch of the tone
when a "ButtonPress" event is sent. It is the
frequency in [Hz].
.RS 7
.PP 
.I Range: 
"0" \- "3000" 
.PP 
.I Default:
"1500" 



.RE
